text: Szymon Sobala (15 January 1919 - 9 May 2009) was a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Piekary Śląskie Category:Sportspeople from Silesian Voivodeship
